---
title: "工具"
breadcrumb:
  - name: "首页"
    href: "/"
  - name: "工具"
    href: "{{ page.url }}"
description: "14 个产品相关工具，覆盖图表、文档、AI 辅助等场景。"
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="page-header">
  <h1>🔧 工具箱</h1>
  <div class="subtitle">14 个产品相关工具，覆盖图表、文档、AI 辅助等场景。</div>
</div>

<div class="tools-list">
  {% for t in tools %}
  <div class="tool-item">
    {% if t.cmd %}<code class="tool-item-cmd">{{ t.cmd }}</code>{% endif %}
    <div>
      <div class="tool-item-name">{{ t.name }}</div>
      <div class="tool-item-desc">{{ t.desc }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="phase-section" style="margin-top:40px;">
  <h2>提示</h2>
  <div class="tip-list">
    <div class="tip-item">
      <code class="tip-skill">/prd</code>
      <span class="tip-desc">最常用——写 PRD、功能文档、需求整理</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-item">
      <code class="tip-skill">/meeting-to-action</code>
      <span class="tip-desc">整理会议纪要，提取行动项</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-item">
      <code class="tip-skill">/obsidian-knowledge-saver</code>
      <span class="tip-desc">沉淀对话内容到知识库</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
